<p>This podcast features guest speaker, Bill Wilson of the Oregon Ministry Network of the Assemblies of God. Bill continues the series highlighting the prophecied return of Christ and the rapture as described in the Bible.</p>
<p>Pastor Ray Noah is the lead pastor of Portland Christian Center and President of Petros Network. &nbsp;</p>
<p>Portland Christian Center is a multigenerational church in the Portland, Oregon area. Attendees come from throughout the greater metro Portland area. &nbsp;Portland Christian Center is known for ministry opportunities for every age.</p>
<p>Petros Network is a church planting and redemptive lift non-profit responsible for planting 3000 churches in the last decade. <a href="http://www.petrosnetwork.org">www.PetrosNetwork.org</a></p></div>